## title

### Source (en)

~~~text
How long will this data set be kept?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
這個資料集會被保留多久？
~~~

## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
For optimum reusability data needs to be available for as long as possible. There may be financial reasons why you can't keep the data any longer; there may be legal, contractual or regulatory reasons requiring you to delete the data.
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
為達到最佳的可再利用性（reusability），資料需盡可能長期維持可取用性。然而，可能因財務因素而無法繼續保存資料；也可能因法律、合約或法規要求，而必須刪除資料。
~~~
